            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "A prompt registry version is as important as a model registry version — it defines half of what your LLM system does. Store prompts as versioned, immutable YAML artifacts, enforce eval gates before promotion, verify content hashes on every load, and tag every production trace with the prompt version so regressions are traceable to their exact source."
